This is a spot-on analysis of the situation and I agree, this definitely sounds like packet loss. There are a number of things that can cause packet loss, however, you'll find the most common solutions listed in our [connection troubleshooting guide. 
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if this helped solve the issue.
